_sText:
This is my first race map to the new rally mod for css.

Info of the map:
- 3 laps with 25 checkpoints/ The average time of the 3 laps is 2:20.00(My best time with no one on the track was 2:13.67 try to beat :P)
- The ready zone
- Gman for spectator zone
- A fun wait zone
- 4 Pit Stops
- Track located in an island

Try the map and hope you enjoy!
Comment, rate and give some feedback so that I may improve the map pls ;)
--------------------------------------
In order to play the map right you need a server with rally mod installed.
